# @pr-fix ‚Äî GitHub PR review fixer

**Invoke:** `@pr-fix` ¬∑ user says `pr-fix PR#129` or pastes a PR URL.

**Canonical command:** `.claude/commands/pr-fix.md` (keep in sync).

**Repo:** `amo-tech-ai/lumina-studio` ¬∑ stack: Next.js `app/`, Mastra, Supabase edge, CopilotKit v2.

**Skill map SSOT:** `tasks/intelligence/ai/skill-map.md` ¬∑ inventory: `.claude/skills/README.md`

---

## Phase 0 ‚Äî Pre-flight (Skills & MCP audit)

Before triage or code, orient on PR domain:

```bash
gh pr view <N> --json number,title,body,headRefName,files
```

1. **Read changed paths** ‚Üí load domain skills (read `SKILL.md`, not memory).
2. **If PR closes IPI-###** ‚Üí read `docs/linear/issues/IPI-<N>-*.md` + run `@task-verifier` before marking merge-ready.
3. **Run `graphify query "<concept>"`** before reading flagged source files.
4. **Output:** one paragraph ‚Äî PR intent, skills loaded, MCP probes planned.

