## Phase 2 ‚Äî Fix

Order: **Bug ‚Üí Refactor ‚Üí Tech debt ‚Üí Style**

1. Checkout PR branch (worktree preferred ‚Äî `worktrees` skill): `ipi/<task>-<slug>`
2. `graphify query "<concept>"` ‚Üí read flagged lines only
3. Re-read loaded domain skill if comment touches patterns (auth, CK v2, Mastra tools)
4. **Smallest safe diff** ‚Äî match file patterns; no drive-by refactors
5. **>3 files** for one finding ‚Üí confirm with user first
6. **One concern per commit** ‚Äî never mix unrelated fixes

### iPix defaults

- Auth: `withOperatorAuth(req)` ‚Üí `OperatorAuthError` ‚Üí 401
- Brand RLS: `createSupabaseServerClient()` (async)
- CopilotKit: `@copilotkit/react-core/v2` only ‚Äî no v1 hooks
- Mastra tools: `tool.execute!()` from routes ‚Äî no raw `generateText` in routes
- Gemini: server-only; default `gemini-3.1-flash-lite` per `gemini` skill
- AI SDK `ai@6.x`: `maxOutputTokens`, not `maxTokens`
- Never `--no-verify` on push
- **Stop** if fix needs a migration ‚Äî report, don't push (use `create-migration` + migration-reviewer)

