## Phase 3 ‚Äî Verify

### 3a. Static

```bash
cd app && npm run typecheck    # must be 0 errors
cd app && npm test             # no new failures vs main
```

| Area | Also run |
|------|----------|
| `app/**` | `npm run lint` |
| routes/config/env/middleware | `npm run build` (needs `DATABASE_URL`) |
| migrations | `infisical run -- npm run supabase:verify-rls` |
| edge fn | `npm run supabase:verify-edge` |
| AI / BI pipeline | `npm run supabase:verify-brand-intelligence` |
| DNA scoring | `npm run supabase:verify-dna` |

Fail ‚Üí stop, do not push.

### 3b. Domain (skills + MCP)

Run probes from Phase 0 matrix. Examples:

- **Supabase:** `execute_sql` on live schema; `npm run supabase:verify-rls`
- **Mastra:** grep agent registry + `searchMastraDocs "<API>"`
- **CopilotKit:** grep v2 imports; check `references/ipix-production.md` for prod 401s
- **Gemini:** confirm model in `app/src/mastra/models.ts` or `_shared/gemini.ts`
- **DESIGN-*** PRs:** `design-md` checklist + token/visual diff vs `tokens.css`
- **UI:** `accessibility` keyboard/contrast spot-check; browser snapshot if visual

### 3c. Spec compliance

If PR closes IPI-###: check each AC in issue md ‚Üí probe ‚Üí result. Any üî¥ = blocker.

Run `@task-verifier` before final merge-ready sign-off.

