## Hard rules

- Never resolve without reading full comment body
- Never claim "already fixed" without reading HEAD at that line (+ MCP for DB)
- Load domain skill before arguing patterns ‚Äî don't cite training data
- Align with `@pr-workflow` ‚Äî all threads resolved or waived before merge
- Docs-only fixes (rules, audit) ‚Üí **separate PR** from code fixes
- One concern per PR/commit ‚Äî never mix unrelated review fixes with feature work
